"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-10-colleges-sending-the-most-athletes-to-the-2024-paris-olympics-01j3dy7vmgwz\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"With the 2024 Summer Olympic Games taking place in Paris in a few days, now may be the time to not only derive some more American pride cheering on your countrymen, but you may also want to freshen up on if any of your favorite colleges have student-athletes going across the pond for the right to compete for Olympic glory.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 51, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999485885767884, \"rank\": 5.141406637428287e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 121, \"end\": 135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Cruise_Lines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2985588551177575e-15, \"text\": \"American pride\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Cruise_Lines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Cruise_Lines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not worry, Reddit CFB had us covered several days ago, you all.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While that social media account over on The X spends most of its time following along with the greatest sport in the world (college football, duh!\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"), it also likes to have fun when all sorts of competitions are happening, athletic or not.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If they could get fired up for America over Fourth of July hot dog consumption, they will get fired up over the Summer Olympic Games and college programs.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here arethe 10 colleges sending the most athletes to the 2024 Paris Olympicsthis summer.\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Keep up with theOlympic medal count by collegeto see which school produced the most podium visits!\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It should be noted that not all of these athletes are on Team USA, but rather the entire Olympic field.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999217770110055, \"rank\": 7.214601657824606e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The NCAA has published an interactive table of all of the member schools sending athletes to the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9775997586875759, \"rank\": 0.022913488217756194, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's a breakdown by school.https://t.co/TwEwDqOTZgpic.twitter.com/YZTCP2HT6e  Let us unpack the 10 universities that are sending over the most athletes to Paris this summer.\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1351, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999485885767884, \"rank\": 5.141406637428287e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"None of the 10 schools listed above should really come as much of a surprise.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of them are former Pac-12 schools (Stanford, USC, Cal, UCLA).\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"score\": 0.9999988604872341, \"rank\": 1.1341458241105912e-06, \"text\": \"Stanford\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\"}, {\"begin\": 1499, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\", \"score\": 0.9986858385478579, \"rank\": 0.0013158230335256545, \"text\": \"USC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of their former commissioners Larry Scott really put an emphasis on Olympic sports in his former league.\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Scott_(sports_administrator)\", \"score\": 0.7248213615790733, \"rank\": 0.28409090909082985, \"text\": \"Larry Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Scott_(sports_administrator)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Scott_(sports_administrator)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It may have contributed to football being bad and basketball being deplorable, as well as the conference dying, but it is what it is...\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Cal and Stanford are now in the ACC, five of the top 10 are now SEC schools (Florida,Texas, LSU,Tennessee, Arkansas).\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Golden_Bears\